{
  "stem": "19055.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this German came, and he came very close, and I was shaking, you know, when you're stand there in the line.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And came next to me, the little boy, and he put a piece of bread in my pocket.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then next day, again, we were in the barrack-- in the barrack, and he would come in and we jumped up.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he said, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I'd remembered his face, this-- this old, wrinkled face, with the big, bushy eyebrows and the pipe, and Popeye.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he did this several times.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Let me finish this story by jumping forward, after maybe a year or two after my liberation, being in Hungary, I picked up a-- a magazine.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't remember, unfortunately, what the name was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Oh, unfortunately, I don't have the magazine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I see a picture of a uniformed German man, with the bushy eyebrows and a pipe.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I said, this is Popeye.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It said, and this German SS sergeant worked for the British intelligence.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So there are some providence somewhere that keeps helping you along.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, what-- what--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All I could see that this-- this wagons with the corpses, and-- and the beatings, and the-- and the people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one day, some planes were flying over the camp, and leaflets were falling down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had severe instructions not to pick up any leaflets under death penalty.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nevertheless, somebody picked it up, and we went to the barrack and-- and read it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was that the Allies broke through in the-- in the Western front.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Aachen, ?] which was a German city was taken by the Allies.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
